	</div><!-- end modern_img_frame -->
 
 <h6>Building Up Your Faith</h6>
 <p>Cross+Word is about much more than just looking at errors. Many Christians don't know what to believe and are not well grounded, but here you can browse helpful studies.</p>
 <p><a href="contents.html"><strong>Be Strengthened →</strong></a></p>
</div><!-- end first one_fourth_column -->

	<div class="one_fourth">
	<div class="modern_img_frame modern_four_col_large">
	<div class="modern_preload_four_col_large">
 	<div class="attachment-fadeIn"><a href="contents.html"><img src="images/finch.jpg" alt="finding good seed" width="190" height="111" /></a></div></div>
	</div><!-- end modern_img_frame -->
 
 <h6>Examining Sound Doctrine</h6>
 <p>One aspect of this website is to look at bible passages afresh and to dig out the essential meaning of those scriptures. Further in-depth articles are on the Birthpangs.org website.</p>
 <p><a href="contents.html"><strong>Be Edified →</strong></a></p>
</div><!-- end second one_fourth_column -->

	<div class="one_fourth">
	<div class="modern_img_frame modern_four_col_large">
