	</div><!-- end modern_img_frame -->
 
 <h6>Warning About Error</h6>
 <p>This website now incorportates many, if not all, of the former Cross+Word articles. They were the product of Tricia Tillin's Discernment Ministry from the mid 1980's to recent years.</p>
 <p><a href="contents.html"><strong>Be Cautioned →</strong></a></p>
</div><!-- end third one_fourth_column -->

