 <h6>Offering Media</h6>
 <p>Sometimes it's good to lighten the mood. There are and will be other bits and pieces of media on the site that will offers news items, curiosities and other ephemera.</p>
 <p><a href="contents.html"><strong>Be Entertained →</strong></a></p>
